                            
                            
********  Welcome To the Guessing Game ********

To play this game you only need to use:
   cd     ls    cat

The goal of the game is to select a name of an animal and
guess the image of the animal from an option of 8 different images.

Instructions:
1. To start the game write  
      Cd game and then ls 
2. Next, select your prefered animal from the list and write 
      cd [Prefered_animal] and then ls
3. Choice one image from the 8 different images and write
      cat [selected_image]
4. Follow the instruction from the image
